title: Dramaturgy
synopsis: An original song by Eve, sung by Hatsune Miku, animated by Mah. Eve's self-cover uses the same animated footage and was released on October 11, 2017. Eve included his self-cover MV on his own self-made record label
related_anime: ['Oki ni Mesu mama', 'Nonsense Bungaku', 'Ano Ko Secret']
